  <text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
    <body>
        <div rend="parallel">
            <lg xml:id="TK604">
<l>kuṭimaṭintu kuṟṟam peruku maṭimaṭintu </l>
<l>māṇṭa vuñaṟṟi lavarkku</l>            
            </lg>
            <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Family (greatness) will be destroyed, and faults will increase, in those men who give way to laziness, and put forth no dignified exertions.</l>
            </lg>
        </div>
    </body>
